title: Sattam
subTitle: Raja and Ravi, two best friends, fall in love with the same girl, Radha. But, trouble ensues when Ravi expects a sacrifice from her, in order to save his best friend.

title: Veetla Eli Veliyila Puli
subTitle: An otherwise confident Purshottaman finds himself completely dominated by his overbearing wife. Desperate to escape his uncomfortable situation, he turns to his colleague, Sivaraman, for help.

title: Vazhkai
subTitle: Betrayed by his household, an unemployed mechanic starts over with his geriatric wife. However, fate finally rewards him by turning his struggles into success and making him a millionaire.

title: Jai Hind
subTitle: After his brother is killed in a terrorist attack, Bharath, a policeman, assures his mother that he will resign. However, when he learns of a secret terrorist organisation he sets out to capture them.

title: Sangamam
subTitle: Selvam, a rural folk artist, falls in love with Abhirami, a classical dancer. However, things become complicated when her father disapproves of their relationship.

title: Thavasi
subTitle: Thavasi is a revered landlord who lives in a small village. However, his life changes drastically when a young man commits suicide due to a misjudgement he makes.

title: Vaazhve Maayam
subTitle: Raja and Devi fall in love with each other and get engaged. However, when Raja learns that he is suffering from cancer, he hides it from Devi and calls off the engagement.

title: Coimbatore Mappillai
subTitle: When Balu moves to the city in search of career opportunities, he falls in love with Sumithra. However, Sumithra's evil cousin, Mahesh, creates a rift between their blooming love.

title: Thalapathi
subTitle: Surya, a courageous man who gets raised in the slums, fights for the rights of the poor. However, he becomes friends with Deva, who hires him as his commander and changes his life completely.

title: Sigappu Rojakkal
subTitle: A young man, traumatised by his past, grows up to despise the opposite sex and exploits them. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with a woman prisoner while in jail.

title: Sigappu Rojakkal
subTitle: A young man, traumatised by his past, grows up to despise the opposite sex and exploits them. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with a woman prisoner while in jail.

title: Endrendrum Kadhal
subTitle: Vijay falls in love with Meenu during a business trip and decides to marry her. However, problems arise when Meenu's brother asks him to leave India and settle in Switzerland with her family.

title: Mannan
subTitle: Krishnan's boss, Shanti, is an autocratic, domineering woman whom he constantly defies. Irked and revengeful, she manipulates his mother who has paralysis and marries him in a bid to control him.

title: Billa
subTitle: When Billa, a don, dies at the hands of ACP Murthy, he is replaced by Ranga, his lookalike, to infiltrate the gang. When Murthy is killed, Ranga is trapped since only Murthy knew the truth.

title: Kaalam Maari Pochu
subTitle: Indra and her three sisters are married off to mediocre men by their patriarchal father. However, he realises their importance when his son stirs discord in the family.

title: Anandha Jodhi
subTitle: Falsely accused of murder, physical education teacher Anand fights to clear his name, teaming up with his lover Jyoti and her brother Ballu, to uncover the truth and prove his innocence.

title: Puthiya Pathai
subTitle: Seetharaman, a violent criminal, starts to change his way and become a better person for Seetha, who he once raped and later married her.

title: Amman Kovil Kizhakale
subTitle: Kanmani plans to teach Chinnamani a lesson by pretending to love him. However, it backfires when he ends up marrying her for vengeance.

title: Kalaignan
subTitle: Inderjeet, a singer, is the primary suspect when his female fans are found murdered by a serial killer. Meanwhile, Divya, the first victim's sister, comes to the city to find the killer.
